e=\"height:2.0074em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">9</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.0074em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">9</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">8</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></details>","rawContent","\nWe have a room made out of 3 squares arranged in an L shape. Two people are placed randomly within it. What’s the probability that they can see each other?\n\n:::solution\n\n**Answer**: $\\frac{8}{9}$\n\nWe split the room into 3 unit squares: A, B, C, where B is the centre square connecting the other two.\n\n**Case 1: Both people in the same square**\n\nIf both people are in the same square, they can always see each other. The combinations are AA, BB, CC.\n\nThe probability of both being in the same square is $\\frac{1}{3}$.\n\n**Case 2: At least one person in square B**\n\nIf at least one person is in square B (the centre), they can always see each other—square B has direct line of sight to both A and C.\n\nThe combinations are AB, BA, BC, CB (excluding BB, which we already counted).\n\nThe probability is $\\frac{4}{9}$.\n\n**Case 3: People in opposite squares (A and C)**\n\nThe remaining probability is $\\frac{2}{9}$ for the combinations AC and CA.\n\nIn this case, whether they can see each other depends on the line of sight between them. We consider adding conceptual walls around square B. If the line of sight passes through square B’s internal walls, they can see each other. If it passes through the L-shape’s outer walls, they cannot.\n\nBy symmetry, there’s an equal chance of the line of sight passing through square B’s walls or the outer walls.\n\nThis means there’s a $\\frac{1}{2}$ chance within the $\\frac{2}{9}$ case that they can see each other—contributing $\\frac{1}{9}$ to the total probability.\n\n**Total probability**\n\n$$\n\\frac{1}{3} + \\frac{4}{9} + \\frac{1}{9} = \\frac{3}{9} + \\frac{4}{9} + \\frac{1}{9} = \\frac{8}{9}\n$$\n\n:::\n","dynamicBlocks",[],"inlineComponents",{}]
